id] (2026-01-20 11:21):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大请问你认为这个调整期会持续到月底吗，还是这周就可能结束了[/quote]<br/>没那么快 至少目前看是这样<br/>GJD既然出手了，就要把这些偷鸡的打怕才行，让他们以后懂要在红线里面做事，不要动不动集体挑战监管<br/>不管是盘面还是线下抓人都是这么表现的，所以还要等一下<br/>完结的标志也很简单，科技+金融集体拉指数起来就是调整结束了", "lou": 261, "content_length": 231, "reply_to": 855196797, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768879566}, {"pid": 855197561, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855197169,45974302,430]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67024871]焦糖奶昔[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:24):[/b]<br/><br/>我反正就正股+期权拿着了&amp;#160;<br/><br/>化工只买了川恒 还是很高的位置进的&amp;#160;[/quote]<br/>反正金属方面 铜我看要避一下，等个释放情绪，金银没什么问题 都没到位置", "lou": 262, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 855197169, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768879626}, {"pid": 855199775, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855198228,45974302,431]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65530853]板栗土豆泥[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:31):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大AI硬不是准备锁了吗，难道记错了[s:ac:喷][/quote]<br/><br/>剩15%仓位 平均70%以上涨幅<br/>没行情我不锁他干什么", "lou": 263, "content_length": 49, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 855198228, "postdatetimestamp": 1768880541}, {"pid": 855199939, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855198870,45974302,432]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66983776]大时代冲冲冲[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:35):[/b]<br/><br/>点数其实感觉差不多了，GJD想要玩下去就是在4035-4070中间选一个位置开始启动。<br/>就是时间上不知道到什么时候了，估计周四？[/quote]<br/><br/>差不多这个时间附近", "lou": 264, "content_length": 23, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 855198870, "postdatetimestamp": 1768880609}, {"pid": 855200020, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 11:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855198925,45974302,432]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66199622]小蝎子ICE2[/uid] (2026-01-20 11:36):[/b]<br/><br/>超短投机会在A股消失吗[/quote]<br/><br/>暂时不会 除非进入到十年长牛第三个周期 那是很久之后的事情了", "lou": 265, "content_length": 61, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 855198925, "postdatetimestamp": 1768880649}, {"pid": 855204773, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 12:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855202418,45974302,433]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38762046]mayuzi[/uid] (2026-01-20 12:01):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202601/20/jmQ1au-ghyuZaT1kSc8-fz.jpg.medium.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>首先 本身看龙虎榜溢价就是一个蠢到极点的事情，这个市场大家都是对手盘，能亮给你看的都是想从你手里掏钱的。<br/>其次 龙虎榜是遗留产物，一时半会不会动的，对于能看懂的其实还是很有参考意义的。特别是大家找朋友阶段。", "lou": 266, "content_length": 205, "reply_to": 855202418, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768882950}, {"pid": 855205159, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 88, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 12:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "大约明后天我会买回游戏ETF 相当于50%仓位做了10个点的倒T<br/>然后继续持仓长线。<br/>所以我就不懂了  这种拿什么亏？怎么亏?", "lou": 267, "content_length": 106, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768883162}, {"pid": 855214262, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 13:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855214041,45974302,438]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-20 13:50):[/b]<br/><br/>券商红了[/quote]<br/>有迹象而已，券商的量不够", "lou": 268, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 855214041, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768888368}, {"pid": 855219605, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 85, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "。。。今天这个不是很正常么，航天和应用的融资盘今天爆仓啊。。。早上卖一次 2点半被迫再卖一次<br/>白线金融守指数 谨慎开仓加<br/>大清早不是说了？所以你们平时都不复盘 也不会看盘 能在这个市场活下来真是奇迹", "lou": 269, "content_length": 185, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768891097}, {"pid": 855220132, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "GJD甚至亲自用ETF告诉大家 最近要调整啦  因为要约束一下太活跃的资金，请大家注意，最近不要太激进<br/>这不是都喊话了么你们还那么激进做什么 这里60%仓位持仓等调整结束不行么", "lou": 270, "content_length": 157, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768891345}, {"pid": 855220453, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855219833,45974302,443]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60099555]咪了个咕[/uid] (2026-01-20 14:39):[/b]<br/><br/>这不有你嘛[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>指数就在4100  再这个地方操作越多错越多 到时候别说我了  财神都救不了", "lou": 271, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 855219833, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768891505}, {"pid": 855220606, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855220313,45974302,443]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-20 14:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 为啥港股也跟着被殴打<br/>理论上港股没这个风险吧 明天有没有拉那边的期望[/quote]<br/>说了 不要去港股 港股是拿来给A股公司去上市的 为了吸引RMB回流投资，主要是为了消耗顺差产生RMB能有地方用<br/>不是给你们去投资的。", "lou": 272, "content_length": 122, "reply_to": 855220313, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768891571}, {"pid": 855221594, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 98, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我都不懂你们为什么这么爱抢反弹  搞得各个都是主力一样，感觉一买进去就能地天？<br/>我就从来没有这种想法<br/>GJD最近要调整 我就仓位小点，GJD说大家开干 我就大胆干进去。<br/>现在谁话事就听谁的，就这么简单。", "lou": 273, "content_length": 182, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768892056}, {"pid": 855222024, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 14:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855221222,45974302,445]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60099555]咪了个咕[/uid] (2026-01-20 14:51):[/b]<br/><br/>尾盘都在猛抄航天，明天看看演什么戏。[/quote]<br/>能演啥 吃了融资盘爆仓的血筹呗<br/>这里不管怎么样都是一个阶段性的底部区间 毕竟连跌这么多天，但是不是底部就能马上反弹的，这里机构要重新做起来，必须要底部反复洗<br/>特别是把那些高位的弄出去才是麻烦。而且还有自救的柚子，这里大家搅在一起又没有合力，散户进去都是死。不管涨还是跌我觉得散户都是死", "lou": 274, "content_length": 281, "reply_to": 855221222, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768892251}, {"pid": 855223641, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 15:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855223123,45974302,447]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66907545]ptydd[/uid] (2026-01-20 15:06):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，想请教一下，这部分可以随时撤退的仓位，包含锁仓的票不，谢谢&amp;#128591;很佩服你们这种大块头也能随时保持仓位灵活[s:a2:poi][/quote]<br/>肯定不包括啊  这部分就是靠高盈利硬吃 也不看 也不动", "lou": 275, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 855223123, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768893002}, {"pid": 855229128, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 15:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "还有哪个前期高标没出狱的？如果全部出狱就应该不压盘了", "lou": 276, "content_length": 52, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768895501}, {"pid": 855229765, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 15:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855229555,45974302,450]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62771233]极地丶之光[/uid] (2026-01-20 15:54):[/b]<br/><br/>还有一个利欧，这是最后一个进去的，没到100%就进去的，惨的一塌糊涂[/quote]<br/><br/>还有一个？那在等一天", "lou": 277, "content_length": 25, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 855229555, "postdatetimestamp": 1768895778}, {"pid": 855246739, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 18:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855245397,45974302,456]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60608517]Jerowe[/uid] (2026-01-20 18:05):[/b]<br/><br/>吉米报销了 比今天亏钱还难受[s:a2:哭][/quote]<br/><br/>刚有点起色 天塌了啊 又浪费库里一个赛季了", "lou": 278, "content_length": 43, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 855245397, "postdatetimestamp": 1768904358}, {"pid": 855259231, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 217, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-20 20:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "最近在严打，你们不要整天 我说了什么 我说了什么<br/>你们把这些东西自己融入自己体系就行了<br/>我还年轻  不太想进去。<br/>我什么都没说过 有什么不懂的看首页帖子", "lou": 279, "content_length": 136, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768913050}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155484, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109184, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "zippo578", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109203, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,627999